item.description: Set type to ‘docs’ if you want to render page outside of configured section or if you render section other than ‘docs’ type = ‘docs’ Set page weight to re-arrange items in file-tree menu (if BookMenuBundle not set) weight = 10 (Optional) Set to ’true’ to mark page as flat section in file-tree menu (if BookMenuBundle not set) bookFlatSection = false (Optional) Set to hide nested sections or pages at that level.
